Global Foundry Crane Market Insights
Foundry Crane Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Foundry Crane Market Overview
The global Foundry Crane market has been steadily expanding, with a market size valued at approximately USD 5.6 billion in 2024. This market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 4.2% during the forecast period, reaching a valuation of USD 7.2 billion by 2030. The increasing demand for high-efficiency cranes in industrial sectors such as metal, automotive, and construction drives this growth. Technological advancements in crane automation and safety features are contributing to this upward trajectory. Furthermore, strong infrastructure investments across emerging economies are also boosting market prospects.

